    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was saving marks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she told us that she don't want all of it, and that she gave us a [INAUDIBLE] [NON-ENGLISH]-- clothing.",
