      "text": "So she gave me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She gave me pencils and-- and crayons and because she know that he likes to [INAUDIBLE] took what I was writing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because one day, I-- I-- we were sitting and I was crying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
