      "text": "Write.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] He gave me a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he gave me a pencil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Write something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the-- the first words-- maybe if you will find somewhere, I-- I believe I gave this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- it's a nice [INAUDIBLE] write.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What shall I write?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I write it was a mother and two children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do whatever I can to-- to help the two children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw every day is worse and worse.",
