    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what do we do here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I tell him, maybe some Jew will come here, will find our papers here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we'll find that your mother and [INAUDIBLE] few was with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the first what I start writing [? over the orphan. ?] From this [INAUDIBLE] many, many times.",
